<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She failed to find love with Locky Gilbert on The Bachelor. </p>

<p>But on Thursday, Maddy Carver revealed that since leaving the Channel 10 dating show, she has found her perfect man. </p>

<p>Appearing on HIT radio program, Jimmy &amp; Nath, the 25-year-old admitted that she is no longer single.  </p>

<p>Loved-up: Appearing on HIT radio program, Jimmy &amp; Nath , Maddy Carver (pictured) admitted that she is no longer single</p>

<p>'I am seeing someone, I am loved-up now,' she said. </p>

<p>'We have known each other for about six years and we went on a date six years ago and we didn't click at all. Then we caught back up and this time something just clicked and it feels right.'  </p>

<p>While she didn't share the name of her new beau, the reality star did reveal that he works as an accounts manager. </p>

<p>Maddy, who was rejected by Locky after failing to receive a single date or group date, also divulged her thoughts on his relationship with winner Irena Srbinovska</p>

<p>Maddy, who was rejected by Locky after failing to receive a single date or group date, also divulged her thoughts on his relationship with winner Irena Srbinovska. </p>

<p>The school teacher said she believes Locky and Irena's relationship is genuine, but admitted she 'can't see them getting married'. </p>

<p>'Locky had all these girls' attention inside the mansion,' Maddy reasoned.</p>

<p>Thoughts: Maddy said she believes Locky and Irena's (pictured) relationship is genuine, but admitted she 'can't see them getting married'</p>

<p>'It would be really hard to go back to life just having one girl, don't you think?' she added.</p>

<p>During last week's gut-wrenching finale, Locky told both Irena Srbinovska and rival Bella Varelis he had fallen in love with them - leading both to believe they had won his heart.</p>

<p>But ultimately, it was down to earth nurse Irena, 31, who stole the burly adventure man's heart - leaving Bella, 25, completely devastated.</p>

<p>She's the one! Irena Srbinovska (left) won Locky Gilbert's (right) heart during Thursday's tense Bachelor finale </p>
